name: Date
description: Contains methods for the Date primitive data type.

adddays(integer).name: addDays
adddays(integer).description: Adds the specified number of additional days to a Date.

addmonths(integer).name: addMonths
addmonths(integer).description: Adds the specified number of additional months to a Date

addyears(integer).name: addYears
addyears(integer).description: Adds the specified number of additional years to a Date

day().name: day
day().description: Returns the day-of-month component of a Date.

dayofyear().name: dayOfYear
dayofyear().description: Returns the day-of-year component of a Date.

daysbetween(date).name: daysBetween
daysbetween(date).description: Returns the number of days between the Date that called the method and the specified date.

daysinmonth(integer,integer).name: daysInMonth
daysinmonth(integer,integer).signature: public static Integer daysInMonth(Integer year, Integer month)
daysinmonth(integer,integer).overrideSignature: public static override Integer daysInMonth(Integer year, Integer month)
daysinmonth(integer,integer).description: Returns the number of days in the month for the specified year and month (1=Jan).

format().name: format
format().description: Returns the Date as a string using the locale of the context user

isleapyear(integer).name: isLeapYear
isleapyear(integer).overrideSignature: public static override Boolean isLeapYear(Integer year)
isleapyear(integer).description: Returns true if the specified year is a leap year.

issameday(date).name: isSameDay
issameday(date).description: Returns true if the Date that called the method is the same as the specified date.

month().name: month
month().description: Returns the month component of a Date (1=Jan).

monthsbetween(date).name: monthsBetween
monthsbetween(date).description: Returns the number of months between the Date that called the method and the specified date, ignoring the difference in days.

newinstance(integer,integer,integer).name: newInstance
newinstance(integer,integer,integer).signature: public static Date newInstance(Integer year, Integer month, Integer day)
newinstance(integer,integer,integer).overrideSignature: public static override Date newInstance(Integer year, Integer month, Integer day)
newinstance(integer,integer,integer).description: Constructs a Date from Integer representations of the year, month (1=Jan), and day.

parse(string).name: parse
parse(string).overrideSignature: public static override Date parse(String stringDate)
parse(string).description: Constructs a Date from a String. The format of the String depends on the local date format.

today().name: today
today().description: Returns the current date in the current user's time zone.

tostartofmonth().name: toStartOfMonth
tostartofmonth().description: Returns the first of the month for the Date that called the method.

tostartofweek().name: toStartOfWeek
tostartofweek().description: Returns the start of the week for the Date that called the method, depending on the context user's locale.

valueof(string).name: valueOf
valueof(string).overrideSignature: public static override Date valueOf(String stringDate)
valueof(string).description: Returns a Date that contains the value of the specified String.

valueof(object).name: valueOf
valueof(object).overrideSignature: public static override Date valueOf(Object fieldValue)
valueof(object).description: Converts the specified object to a Date. Use this method to convert a history tracking field value or an object that represents a Date value.

year().name: year
year().description: Returns the year component of a Date
